## Success criteria

<!-- Bullet, checkable. Engineering: tests/lint pass, feature observable.
     Generative: a geometry deliverable (nearest verified landmarks, gap shape,
     promising bridges, small-case evidence) — never a "solved/unsolved" verdict. -->
- `solveSchroederHalfIterate` returns exact `Rational` coefficients for hyperbolic fixed points (no float drift in the symbolic path).
- New unit tests cover at least 3 worked examples and pass under `npm run lint`.
- `HANDOFF.md` is truthful: completion is gated on the tests, not self-report (plan R2).

## Constraints

<!-- Hard boundaries the harness must respect. -->
- No new runtime dependencies; match the vanilla-JS style in `js/engine.js`.
- Keep exact BigInt arithmetic in coefficient paths — never introduce floating point.
- Workers edit only inside their own worktree; never force-push shared branches.
- Stay within `config/budget.json` wall-clock targets (proxy governance, plan §9).
